br />\n一世都記得，諗起條鬚都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46dd05962e739db45b059eac4b875dafc16f66cc","tid":2207832,"uid":215026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:29:13.000Z","msg":"仲試過叫外賣，碗湯一飲落去有洗潔精，我慣左食完飯先飲湯，第一啖已經唔對路，問個同事，佢先話係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢已經飲左大半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後半年我都唔太敢飲餐廳啲湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c9a33cc5ef122a910849197ba830e0a8064310","tid":2207832,"uid":315263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a3f373c6a8f3ba2c7443c4dd4ed267d1d0661f","tid":2207832,"uid":34138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f855772ca1f25ef5f4afe194c0a9bca2acd2ba9","tid":2207832,"uid":315263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">新北江車仔麵，有原隻曱甴</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"係咪執柒左既藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"值得表揚<br />\n燉奶佬上電梯 <br />\n而家係燒味舖個位 <br />\n執咗好耐 <br />\n唔知叫咩名"},{"pid":"aa0b38be8b76e93fb299bb22b2d5e888d2ebe793","tid":2207832,"uid":203748,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3cee70e2e4ba2f6f90b4f42154afbfa378f3df3e","tid":2207832,"uid":42396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"食過間茶記有隻超大老鼠係地下行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cst48Dp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCst48Dp.jpg&h=84adf5fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff320